website_summaries.verdict: Whether your dog has grain allergies or you simply want to feed it a high protein, natural diet, this meaty feast is a great option.
pros: Boasts a higher than average protein content sourced from premium, easily identifiable meats
Grain-free recipe is suitable for dogs with allergies
Premium ingredients with no fillers or additives
100% natural recipe contains no artificial preservatives, colors, or flavors
cons: Needs to be opened with a can opener

website_summaries.verdict: If you are looking for gluten-free canned food to feed by itself or mix with kibble, this is the one to pick. Made by a brand that's known for its quality ingredients.
pros: Most dogs can't resist the flavor of this canned gluten-free dog food that's packed with high-quality ingredients
Made with omega fatty acids, probiotics and prebiotics – ingredients that combine to contribute to overall good health
Great to mix with dry food
cons: Some reports of dents and damage upon arrival
Could get expensive as a sole source of food for a large dog

customer_reviews.author: Cornelia

customer_reviews.title: Good Stuff
customer_reviews.text: I haven't tried it myself, but the dogs seem to think it's great. Judging by the label and what it looks and smells like, I'd say they are right about it. No strange stink when it comes out of the can. Meat looks like meat and not some sort of industrial waste.
customer_reviews.author: Uncle Bob

customer_reviews.title: 3/4 of the cans were severely dented
customer_reviews.text: I received this canned food and 3/4 of the cans were severely dented. None of them were dented to the point where they leaked or the seal was compromised but they are nearly impossible to open with the can opener. They weren't advertised as being damaged and there is no price break so I don't feel it is acceptable to receive them in this condition.
customer_reviews.author: Dawn

customer_reviews.title: Good food but over priced

customer_reviews.text: I've been buying it for months, and dog loves it, but sometimes food is too soft and creamy and many cans have arrived crushed.

customer_reviews.title: Good food
customer_reviews.text: Good product but if your dog has been on dry food only for a while (that means more than one month) give a small quantity to start. This product contains flax seed with can act as a laxative to some. It sure did mine! Once i cut back on this and dry, things went back to normal.

customer_reviews.title: The best of the best! A+++++
customer_reviews.text: Wellness Core grain free is the absolute best wet food you can feed your dog. To my knowledge, it has the highest amount of protein of all canned dog food. My dogs love it, and I mean they go crazy for it and devour their dinner whenever I mix this stuff with their dry food. This product is also suitable for dogs of all life stages, including puppies, which is not the case with most canned dog food. It is expensive but worth the money. Wellness is a fantastic brand, free of by-products, bad preservatives and animal digest, which anyone in their right mind would not want to feed their dogs. A+++++
customer_reviews.author: L. BLOUIN

customer_reviews.title: Dogs Love It.
customer_reviews.text: Have been using Core products for several years. I supplement dry food with a little canned food and I prefer grain free for my dogs. I've priced compared in several locations and I have not found a better deal anywhere else.

product_meta.title: Wellness CORE Natural Grain Free Wet Canned Dog Food
product_meta.description: Flavor Name:Turkey Liver & Chicken Liver| Size:12.5 oz (Pack of 12)Wellness CORE Natural Grain Free Wet Canned Dog Food Turkey, Chicken & Turkey Liver Recipe is healthy, 100% natural gluten free, grain free dog food for adult dogs made with turkey, chicken liver and turkey liver, salmon oil, cranberries and botanicals to help support inner wellness and fortified with vitamins and minerals, including fish and flax omega blend for healthy skin and coat. Each wet canned dog food can be served as a complete, balanced meal or can be added on top for an extra boost of protein. Wellness CORE grain free dog food formulas are based on the nutritional philosophy that dogs thrive on a diet mainly comprised of meat. Each grain free, nutrient-rich formula provides high quality protein for your dog.
feature_bullets: ADVANCED NATURAL NUTRITION TO FUEL YOUR DOGS BEST LIFE: Premium protein expertly balanced with nutrient rich superfoods for a complete and balanced dog food, with the nutrients your dog needs to thrive and no fillers
SAVORY FOOD DOGS LOVE: Wellness CORE is available in grain and grain free recipes, as well as limited ingredient diets for dogs with food sensitivities

LEANER BODY MASS AND MUSCLE TONE: This recipe is made with a high concentration of protein from fresh meat ingredients; contains no meat byproducts, wheat, corn, soy, artificial colors, flavors or preservatives
WHOLE BODY HEALTH: Premium, nutrient rich ingredients and guaranteed mineral levels support strong immune systems, optimal energy, digestive health and healthy skin and coat

WELLNESS NUTRITION: Created by nutritionists, veterinarians and animal lovers, our recipes provide an ideal balance of nature's finest ingredients, carefully selected to nourish and sustain your pet's wellbeing
PASSIONATE ABOUT PETS: Proudly made in North America using only the finest globally sourced ingredients, by a family owned company with a passion for crafting the best food for pets
